    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint retains a strong shine, though you will find some expected minor signs of use such as small stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches that are visible upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and some minor scuffing on the door sills. Mechanically, the car is sound and performs reliably, having undergone regular servicing. It represents a solid, honest example of a cared-for vehicle that is ready for many more miles.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly starter vehicle? This car has plenty of character and is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little DIY! It shows significant wear and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, but it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the usual cost. Grab a bargain and make it your own!",
